Installation:

git clone <GIT-ADDRESS> ~/.vim

Create relative symlinks:

ln -s .vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s .vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

Remember to add the ignore=dirty option to each submodule you add, as
the helptags will dirty those directories.  See .gitmodules for an example.
